g og at man tar de n\u00f8dvendige forh\u00e5ndsregler, sier Jacobsen."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "a1dc993736609ebe3d8661c041d5c8813b9ec8551a0fe1ba7767367dffe64791"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-05T08:45:57.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Psykologiprofessor Karl Henry Jacobsen oppfordrer foreldre til \u00e5 fortelle barn om terrortrusselen."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9952112.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Karl%20Jacobsen%2001.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/c3b28ce8ecdbda1555b00fefdfac8a3078af06e1.jpg?598ccbb3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Ikke sk\u00e5n barna -adressa.no", "Oppr\u00f8rende \u00e5 ikke vite", "- Trusselen en tydelig realitet"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "c3b28ce8ecdbda1555b00fefdfac8a3078af06e1"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "family-and-parenting"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["barn", "skje", "sk\u00e5n barna"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "politidirektoratet og justis"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["syria", "trondheim", "oslo", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "karl henry jacobsen"}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/innenriks"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9952112.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Karl%20Jacobse